channel.title: My 1987 550 Kawasaki stand up jet ski
channel.description:
I went on a 8 hour trip to pick up this beast.
I dunno why but it sorta looks pinkish in these pictures. :\ Its red for sure.
[IMG]http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f304/surfdude2012/standup1.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f304/surfdude2012/standup2.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f304/surfdude2012/standup3.jpg[/img]
[IMG]http://i50.photobucket.com/albums/f304/surfdude2012/standup4.jpg[/img]
Its just a stock 550 at the moment. But i'm planning on putting a new pipe and such on it.
